{"tid":2195574,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌！唔撚食吉野家！我自己整煎雞野菜飯！","createTime":"2020-09-09T09:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T01:22:51.000Z","uid":68594,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"42f9ebec3beb0c42c4e6379f608a0f804e1d297d","tid":2195574,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係子言張！<br />\n<br />\n我都差唔多有一年半冇食過吉野家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然之間好想食佢個煎雞野菜飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味唔想幫襯佢，我決定自己整！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8ck2XMIPhSk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8ck2XMIPhSk&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=4a5a1605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8ck2XMIPhSk</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴材料<br />\n雞排................2塊<br />\n西蘭花.............1棵<br />\n甘筍.................1條<br />\n蔥....................1棵<br />\n<br />\n🔴調味料<br />\n日本豉油、燒肉汁、紹興酒/米酒、胡椒粉、鹽、糖、雞粉、生粉<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n🔴步驟<br />\n1.雞排去冰後用紙巾印乾<br />\n2.雞排加入調味料：半蓋紹興酒、兩湯匙燒肉汁、一蓋日本豉油、少許鹽、兩匙生粉、一匙糖<br />\n(醃雞排的汁不用倒掉，可用作製作燒汁)<br />\n3.撈勻後放入雪櫃冷藏30分鐘或以上<br />\n4.西蘭花用花的部分切成細塊、甘筍上切一些坑紋並切成薄片、蔥切成蔥花<br />\n5.準備一鍋水，加入一匙鹽，加熱至水滾<br />\n6.倒入西蘭花及甘筍片汆水，煮兩至三分鐘後撈起備用<br />\n7.煎鑊冷鑊落油，油熱後放入雞排，先煎雞皮那一邊，煎至金黃色<br />\n8.雞排翻面後轉細火，冚蓋焗8-9分鐘，夾起備用<br />\n9.準備醬汁： 倒入一碗水、三匙糖、醃雞排的汁、一圈日本豉油、一匙雞粉、少許胡椒粉<br />\n10.調較好味道後倒入生粉水，煮至滾起及變得濃稠<br />\n11.把雞排切塊，把雞排、西蘭花、甘筍鋪上白飯<br />\n12.淋上醬汁及灑上蔥花<br />\n<br />\n最後！鍾意我呢段片嘅朋友可以俾個like我啦或者可以訂閱我嘅Channel嘅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n►訂閱我：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E5%AD%90%E8%A8%80%E5%BC%B5&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=cf97ed97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張</a>"},{"pid":"f8b3e1927ad2f793ae822d777fcc688b02f04dbd","tid":2195574,"uid":254967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cad658e62a7dc856a6f71a30259988c8185f8bc7","tid":2195574,"uid":366500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed13dd5e70a3c7de791d11019bbeae0c3751be8b","tid":2195574,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"當年中學用佢呢個餐食晏減肥<br />\n屌依家藍店不了"},{"pid":"e0335a3b84bf596073a60ce4fa5fb33716e7483c","tid":2195574,"uid":366500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdd30c62b0a0ee0c10c02da896e9488aa4c7448","tid":2195574,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8b3e1927ad2f793ae822d777fcc688b02f04dbd","tid":2195574,"uid":254967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"最緊要簡單，自己煮都好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6810997fbc343bb1785bb39222ff888dc4b85c6","tid":2195574,"uid":366500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed13dd5e70a3c7de791d11019bbeae0c3751be8b","tid":2195574,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"當年中學用佢呢個餐食晏減肥<br />\n屌依家藍店不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\